What you need to know:

In 2008,  K’Ogalo under the tutelage of James Siang’a (R.I.P.) was building a youthful squad after the club went for over a decade without winning the Kenyan Premier League (KPL) titleA similar scenario will play out on Saturday as former Gor Mahia talisman Jacques Tuyisenge will be turning out for APR just a year after leaving K’OgaloGor Mahia defender and assistant captain Philemon Otieno says they are ready for the must-win encounter